[30;1m564 | [0m[35m/// The input to the algorithm is a graph. If the graph is bipartite, the[0m
[30;1m565 | [0m[35m/// output is an assignment of colors to the edges of the graph so that[0m
[30;1m566 | [0m[35m/// no two incident edges have the same color. The algorithm runs in[0m
